  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To study the demographic characteristic of patients with necrotizing soft tissue infections.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      At Aarhus University Hospital, Denmark, all patients with necrotizing soft tissue infections&#xD;
      will be registered in a database in order to be able to describe their symptoms, demographic&#xD;
      variables and thier treatment (surgery, time to surgery, antibiotics, intensive care unit,&#xD;
      laboratory data etc).&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
